title._content: Old Coal Company Store Which Was Gutted by Fire in the Fentress County, Tennessee, Town of Wilder near Cookeville 04/1974

description._content: Original Caption: Old Coal Company Store Which Was Gutted by Fire in the Fentress County, Tennessee, Town of Wilder near Cookeville.
